precis:
Enactment of the GASOLINE AND GASOLINE BLEND DISPENSING FLOW RATE
REGULATIONS which prohibit gasoline retailers and fleet-volume consumers
from using a nozzle to dispense gasoline if the flow rate from the nozzle
exceeds 38 litres per minute.
